title: Euro Cuisine Yogurt Maker
description:
Make homemade, all-natural, rich and creamy yogurts with any kind of milk (including soy) in just 6--8 hours. Easy-to-use maker allows you to control sweetness, ingredients and fat content. As you can prepare up to two quarts of yogurt at a time, the unit is very economical. Cook up enough yogurt for a whole week's worth of enjoyment in one batch.

To purchase the products featured, please visit: http://www.surlatable.com/product/PRO-693937/Euro-Cuisine-Yogurt-Maker
